      <title>殼牌第一季獲利超預期 77 億美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-beats-expectations-with-77-bln-first-quarter-profit-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[殼牌週四公佈第一季調整後獲利為 77 億美元，大幅超出預期，得益於強勁的石油交易和更高的煉油利潤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-beats-expectations-with-77-bln-first-quarter-profit-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 06:06:08 GMT</pubDate>
