      <title>日本住友商事淨利下降32%，未達預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-sumitomo-corp-net-profit-down-32-misses-estimates-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本住友商事株式會社報告稱，截至 3 月的財年淨利潤較上年同期下降 31.7%，至 3,864 億日圓（合 25 億美元），低於預期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-sumitomo-corp-net-profit-down-32-misses-estimates-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:37:18 GMT</pubDate>
