    <item>
      <title>諾和諾德上調肥胖藥物需求推動的前景</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/obesity-drugmaker-novo-nordisks-q1-profit-beats-forecast-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麥製藥商諾和諾德(Novo Nordisk) 週四上調了2024 年的前景，並實現了好於預期的季度利潤，這家丹麥製藥商競相提高其廣受歡迎的減肥藥Wegovy 的產量，並抵禦競爭對手禮來(Eli Lilly) 的競爭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/obesity-drugmaker-novo-nordisks-q1-profit-beats-forecast-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:34:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
